{"tid":785802,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[physics jj入] 嚟條問題我屈埋屈埋好耐！！！！！！！","createTime":"2018-08-19T13:18:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-20T15:23:57.000Z","uid":199211,"like":0,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"21e58dfcbc9788b53e6a948c11c3fe41319e55df","tid":785802,"uid":199211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T13:18:25.000Z","msg":"hi 又係我 之前喺學術台問熱能俾人負皮嗰個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 今次大家屌細力啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n話說你係一個太空人 喺地球帶左一罐熱既氣體上太空<br />\n然後就喺太空放啲熱空氣出嚟 咁大家就知道gas 會diffusion 由於太空又大又無其他氣體 該團熱氣好快就由彈嚟彈去既粒子 變成以直線飛行既粒子（無野撞佢就唔會改變方向）<br />\n<br />\n咁我想問啲粒子仲熱唔熱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  (記得上個po 有巴打話一粒粒子係無溫度） 所以提左個咁既situation <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61cb402913732846356381a733c0c6bb910e7612","tid":785802,"uid":12633,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T13:20:00.000Z","msg":"Definition of temperature"},{"pid":"a7208978f5afcf396f6833efe558120fc97f1257","tid":785802,"uid":199211,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"61cb402913732846356381a733c0c6bb910e7612","tid":785802,"uid":12633,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T13:20:00.000Z","msg":"Definition of temperature"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T13:21:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50e24e87b137e152264bd961e23eb94f92c00f00","tid":785802,"uid":199211,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T13:23:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93ca456402246c802794da76af1b7ffd3c19c586","tid":785802,"uid":102372,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T13:24:42.000Z","msg":"粒子有兩種情況係有溫度<br />\n1) 有motion/ collision <br />\n2) 自己有vibration <br />\n而energy係唔會被消失，只會被transfer <br />\n其他自己諗"},{"pid":"b18051cbfc2dd7156dab67a2c1a6731d334e5226","tid":785802,"uid":102372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T13:26:40.000Z","msg":"你也可以去睇下咩係絕對零度"},{"pid":"cb1045689f64bd5dd0e3568ebca5ddb1570f7d40","tid":785802,"uid":140830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T13:26:46.000Z","msg":"巴打呢個situation 我哋只會諗個別particle 嘅kinetic energy . <br />\n<br />\nNot average kinetic energy"},{"pid":"df8d13a179a25f106579e2af0628c44abbe9ceb7","tid":785802,"uid":34771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T13:28:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hyperphysics.phy-astr.gsu.edu/hbase/thermo/heat.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhyperphysics.phy-astr.gsu.edu%2Fhbase%2Fthermo%2Fheat.html&d=1lCqc%2Bpq6fJsAPOhlIaZW0bWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=c415515c\" target=\"_blank\">http://hyperphysics.phy-astr.gsu.edu/hbase/thermo/heat.html</a><br />\n<br />\n自修下先<br />\n<br />\n乜都唔識好難答你"},{"pid":"05873b454ea5a34ab342b21cec2378b6d87c306c","tid":785802,"uid":102372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cb1045689f64bd5dd0e3568ebca5ddb1570f7d40","tid":785802,"uid":140830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T13:26:46.000Z","msg":"巴打呢個situation 我哋只會諗個別particle 嘅kinetic energy . <br />\n<br />\nNot average kinetic energy"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T13:34:40.000Z","msg":"KE 轉為Heat energy係因為有drag , 所以係太空佢V係唔會變，咁姐係無energy轉